    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E92 M3, a definitive example of naturally aspirated precision. This specimen features the S65 4.0L V8, delivering a linear power band culminating at an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable: rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively addressed using OEM+ components. The chassis retains its factory-fresh rigidity, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) that provides immediate feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior's Novillo leather shows zero bolster wear, reflecting its meticulous preservation. A purist\u2019s specification in turn-key condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
