      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections, while the interior remains a sanctuary of pristine leather and untouched surfaces, still retaining that signature new-car scent. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standard with a comprehensive, documented service history. This is a rare, time-capsule example for the buyer who demands perfection. The sale includes all original keys, factory manuals, and the original window sticker.",
